comments: Matthews (MIL) cleanly dislodges the ball from DeRozan (CHI) as he gathers and enters his upward shooting motion during his jump shot attempt.
The ball is last touched by Matthews (MIL) before going out of bounds.
Matthews (MIL) initiates body contact with DeRozan (CHI) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) reaches in and initiates contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that he is able to move through and make his intended pass.
Williams (CHI) reaches in and makes contact to Lopez's (MIL) arm as he enters his upward shooting motion during his driving shot attempt.
While defending Caruso (CHI) on the perimeter, Connaughton (MIL) reaches in, but does not make contact to Caruso's arm as he is dribbling.
While dribbling on the perimeter, Caruso (CHI) does not dislodge Connaughton (MIL) from his defensive position.
DeRozan (CHI) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps into his jump shot attempt.
Holiday (MIL) makes incidental contact with DeRozan's (CHI) hand that does not affect his ability to follow through during the jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (MIL) and absorbs the contact.
Connaughton (MIL) grabs DeRozan (CHI) attempting to commit a take foul.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by DeRozan (CHI).
Both Lopez (MIL) and Vucevic (CHI) make incidental contact with each other while pursuing the loose ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) swings his arms into Caruso (CHI) and initiates contact that dislodges him from his legal guarding position.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Williams (CHI) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
DeRozan (CHI) makes contact with Allen's (MIL) arm that affects his shot near the rim.  The foul occurs before the expiration of the game clock.
